What is a race condition? How will you find and solve race condition show with proper running code ?


RACE-CONDITION IN JAVA:-
                         
Race condition occurs when more than one thread are trying to access the same method (a part of program which are shared by them)
this is incorrect behavior of program;

For example one thread is reading data from linked list and other thread is trying to delete the same data;
this process leads to race condition;

To solve problem of data inconsistency due to race conditIon  java uses SYNCHRONIZED KEYWORD;